{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About This Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Battle of Orks</i> is a shared-screen co-op game that blends orks with slot machine mechanics! Summon your orks, enter the fray, and lead your team to victory!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Distinctive Orks with Unique Styles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>The Battle of Orks</i>, you\u2019ll build your team from a unique cast of orks before each battle. Each ork belongs to a clan, and picking a clan \u201cleader\u201d will grant powerful bonuses to help shape your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/1.gif?t=1733829325\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real-Time Competition of Strategy and Luck</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The rules are simple: pull the lever to summon orks! But winning takes a clever strategy\u2014place double bets at key moments to score more coins and maximize your rewards. Landing three  three matching symbols might even summon a special ork, whose skills and buffs can shift the battle in your favor. Stay sharp and use them wisely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/2.gif?t=1733829325\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Just Click!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When Unlimited Time mode kicks in, forget all the rules and just click! ! ! The faster you click, the more orks charge into battle, overwhelming your opponent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/3.gif?t=1733829325\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akam